7. **Recipe/entry UX unification:** Add Entry was brought closer to Add Recipe and contextual actions were cleaned up.
8. **Core app shell:** dashboard sections, Settings, themes, units, export/import, daily targets, date switching, and live version/build display are in place.
9. **Supplement tracking foundation:** dedicated supplement tracking flow is now in place, including working supplement/stacks logging behavior.
10. **Form polish foundation:** editable event time and scroll-to-error behavior are in place.

### Future work
1. **Calorie + electrolyte truth pass:** verify calorie behavior and improve sodium/potassium target/reference clarity.
2. **Exercise + trend polish:** refine exercise UX and continue interaction polish on the shared chart system.
3. **Shared form + feedback polish:** keep validation, save feedback, and edge-case form behavior clean and obvious.
4. **Settings + personalization cleanup:** keep Settings organized and prevent future junk-drawer creep.
5. **Recipe library usefulness pass:** seed more real recipes and improve real-world browsing/filter usefulness.
6. **Later reassessment:** reprioritize after more real-device use.

